This project contains software only. It does not redistribute ECMWF ERA5 data.

Users who download reanalysis data via this tooling must comply with:

- ECMWF ERA5 terms of use: https://www.ecmwf.int/en/forecasts/datasets/reanalysis-datasets/era5
- AWS Open Data Registry terms for ARCO ERA5 on Google Cloud Storage
- Copernicus Climate Data Store terms when using the optional CDS backend

When publishing work based on data prepared with these scripts, cite ERA5
(Hersbach et al., 2020) and document your bounding box, date range, and script version.
